{"tid":290980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小販用狗肉冒充沙爹雞串 遊客唔知仲食得好滋味","createTime":"2017-06-20T07:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T12:45:51.000Z","uid":13468,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7162e8303298e4a2d51f0d0d89c435d12bda0fee","tid":290980,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:56:00.000Z","msg":"小販用狗肉冒充沙爹雞串 遊客唔知仲食得好滋味<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170620/56851257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170620%2F56851257&d=V27aFpDl%2FZ2sWc8gXS%2BDudtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=0fedbe3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170620%2F56851257&h=a96596f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170620/56851257</a><br />\n<br />\n外國遊客到印尼峇里享受陽光與海灘時，可能試過享用當地小販兜售的燒肉串，但澳洲動物協會（Animals Australia）發現，竟有無良商人用狗肉冒充雞肉賣給遊客。調查人員指，這些狗肉有可能涉及食物安全風險。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲動物協會早前向印尼峇里的肉市場展開4個月調查，揭發無良商人在旅遊區沙米亞克（Seminyak）的Double Six沙灘販賣狗肉。<br />\n<br />\n短片可見一名男子拿起裝滿狗肉沙嗲串的膠盒向遊客兜售：「只需一元&hellip;&hellip;沙嗲雞串&hellip;&hellip;不是狗肉。」有遊客回應說：「只要不是狗肉就行了。」便買了串燒，後來亦有一群澳洲遊客「食過返尋味」再買幾串。但當調查人員上前向小販查問時，小販卻承認沙嗲串是狗肉做的。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲動物協會在旅遊區幾街之隔的地方，發現有狗隻被吊起來殺死，最後被製成狗肉。一位名叫路克（Luke）的調查員曾目擊狗隻被人毒打致死，甚至毒死。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲動物協會總監懷特（Lyn White）直指，狗肉交易已令有毒的肉類流入市場，造成食物安全問題，她說：「狗隻的遭遇已令人髮指，遊客也渾然不知自己助長了狗肉交易。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》／Animals Australia"},{"pid":"65652981db5fd6e186aa11d3350bd3abc9cc7cbf","tid":290980,"uid":48631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:01:40.000Z","msg":"咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a82ad15401b43c679b07da4a5ebc0605ce6b0e","tid":290980,"uid":68491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:25:08.000Z","msg":"狗肉同雞肉都食唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔撚同口感"},{"pid":"6a2837c279b1a7e817b9b6f79634586256c2140b","tid":290980,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗肉同雞肉都食唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔撚同口感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n掛雞頭賣狗肉"},{"pid":"ff5964ffaf8d166bb4c29decd45414d376fa83a2","tid":290980,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗肉同雞肉都食唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔撚同口感</blockquote><br />\n一種紅肉一種白肉<br />\n你話扮豬牛羊都話<br />\n<br />\n扮雞肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94eca4a630fca6d45549770806be528e389576d","tid":290980,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:30:18.000Z","msg":"食狗撚又贏"},{"pid":"954c613cbbeae0ec2311098ace770e8946a85aaa","tid":290980,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac2894d23322387c6ff9228ce87927c6b82b8f3","tid":290980,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:42:03.000Z","msg":"36滾一滾 耶穌都企唔穩"},{"pid":"33e63e0e64e5729955f6ba64e9979df011830432","tid":290980,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:28:11.000Z","msg":"狗肉有種好獨特既味道，有養狗都應該聞得出"},{"pid":"20d94285782c9c079ea6ece35ffbec45ee4ad60e","tid":290980,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗肉有種好獨特既味道，有養狗都應該聞得出</blockquote><br />\n落咗好多孜然粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa625ff630693f8a3a897f81417057ddb6c7c8b","tid":290980,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:37:42.000Z","msg":"乜係峇里d雞仲貴過狗既咩"},{"pid":"29e6bb12b0f25b823ec1b56981ba10bc53c129f6","tid":290980,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜係峇里d雞仲貴過狗既咩</blockquote><br />\n喺條街求其落藥都毒得死狗<br />\n肯執就得<br />\n金錢上成本就係買包老鼠藥嘅錢<br />\n買雞平得過買包老鼠藥？"}]}